                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote scribe="JonErl001" scope="major" script="textualis">
                                <p> Written, apart from fol. <locus>12</locus> , by Jón Erlendsson
                                    from <name type="place">Villingaholt</name> in a
                                    clear seventeenth-century Gothic book hand. </p>
                            </handNote>
                            <handNote scribe="unknown" scope="minor" script="humbook">
                                <p>Fol. 12 has been added later to replace a missing leaf; the hand
                                    is younger but appears consciously to imitate the hand of the
                                    main scribe.</p>
                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>
