                                    century</origDate> by <name type="person" key="JonErl001">Sr.
                                    Jón Erlendsson</name> . </p>
                        </origin>
                        <acquisition>
                            <p> According to the accompanying slip, Árni Magnússon borrowed the
                                manuscript from <name type="person" key="JonTho012">Jón
                                    Þorláksson</name> in <date when="1709">1709</date> and then
                                purchased it from him in <date when="1710">the following year</date>
                                . </p>
